{"tid":725551,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"馬勒當拿向拉莫斯道歉：我道歉 但你就不是最佳","createTime":"2018-07-01T17:21:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T10:13:19.000Z","uid":147522,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"69f7da7c232b290c67fde383ac0015dcba6bbc56","tid":725551,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T17:21:23.000Z","msg":"　　世界盃開戰以來，球王馬勒當拿成為場外最受關注的熱點之一，他同西班牙大將拉莫斯的罵戰也引來人們的關注和討論。不過，如今老馬卻意外地向拉莫斯道歉。<br />\n<br />\n　　此前馬勒當拿曾公開稱「拉莫斯不是世界最佳中堅，高甸才是」，而拉莫斯則反擊稱「馬勒當拿根本不是阿根廷隊史最佳，美斯才是」，雙方的口水大戰愈演愈烈。<br />\n<br />\n　　<br />\n　　不過現在，馬勒當拿想要終結這場鬧劇了，老馬稱：「如果拉莫斯想要我道歉，那我就向他道歉。但是，我絕不會改變我對足球純粹的想法。拉莫斯是一個出色的球員，一個偉大的隊長，他能成為一個很好的領袖，我們也能在皇馬陣中看到這一點。但是，對我來說，他根本不是最佳中堅！」<br />\n　　「你們都很清楚，對我來說，我被從不在乎別人的看法，我的想法是自由的。因此，如果拉莫斯感覺被冒犯了，那我道歉，但是我不會改變自己的想法。」"},{"pid":"6e3edaf781872218f5e6aadb22db001d789987dd","tid":725551,"uid":82895,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T09:06:23.000Z","msg":"撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeac6b51e20071b99b2a8ad62290fbad412a3f66","tid":725551,"uid":99700,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T09:13:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/NINTCHDBPICT000416348879-e1530043836366.jpg?strip=all&amp;quality=100&amp;w=1200&amp;h=800&amp;crop=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2FNINTCHDBPICT000416348879-e1530043836366.jpg%3Fstrip%3Dall%26quality%3D100%26w%3D1200%26h%3D800%26crop%3D1&h=755835ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0bda74d25c5afb4e772d429e0227121f2ac8cdba","tid":725551,"uid":35176,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T09:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/02/175010_c64ba06c47f91c6952b493d00ecdb920.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net